cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on learning sensorimotor patterns of a robot to achieve a task. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as Gaussian processes are used for learning the sensorimotor mapping. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper proposes an autonomous framework for achieving a task. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is possible as the framework involves learning from high-dimensional sensory spaces. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also possible as the paper discusses long-term planning and generating a sequence of states to achieve a goal.
